埃迪·范·海伦死前服用了一整瓶类固醇药，因为它们让他“感觉像超人” https://www.nme.com/news/music/eddie-van-halen-took-whole-bottle-of-steroid-pills-before-death-as-they-made-him-feel-like-superman- 3806572?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=eddie-van-halen-在死前拿了一整瓶类固醇药丸，因为他们让他感觉像超人Max PilleySat, 26 Oct 2024 21:29:30 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3806572 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位传奇吉他手在脑瘤切除手术后服用了止痛药</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eddie-van-halen-took-whole-bottle-of-steroid-pills-before-death-as-they-made-him-feel-like-superman-3806572">埃迪·范·海伦 (Eddie Van Halen) 在去世前服用了一整瓶类固醇药丸，因为它们让他“感觉像超人”，</a>这一帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eddie_van_halen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eddie-van-halen">埃迪·范·海伦</a>在去世前不久服用了一整瓶类固醇药，因为他喜欢它们给他的“超人感觉”。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="607" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/eddie-van-halen-obituary-tribute-2774589"><b>埃迪·范·海伦 (Eddie Van Halen)，1955 年至 2020 年：将吉他独奏变成烟火表演的巨人</b></a></li></ul><p>这位传奇吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/eddie-van-halen-obituary-tribute-2774589">因喉癌并发症于 2020 年 10 月去世，</a>享年 65 岁。</p><p>现在，他的兄弟亚历克斯（与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/van-halen">范·海伦</a>一起打鼓）在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/alex-van-halen-eddie-van-halen-brothers-book-interview-1235129960/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《滚石》杂志</i></a>采访时透露，埃迪服用这些药物并不是为了伤害自己，而是为了追求他认为药物会给他带来的感觉。</p><p>亚历克斯解释说，埃迪服用这些药丸是为了对抗脑肿瘤切除手术后的肿胀。 “常识不是埃德的强项，”他说。 “如果两个好的话，二十个更好。这是我们的座右铭。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DBZFq5lxaoR/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="d